column1: On March 17, 2014, the Federal Reserve conducted a fixed-rate offering of term deposits through its Term Deposit Facility.The operation offered seven-day term deposits at an interest rate of 0.26000 percent. Following are the results of the operation:
column6: The awarded deposits will settle on March 20, 2014, and will mature on March 27, 2014.The interest rate of 0.26000 percent will apply to all awarded deposits.
